Chicken, chopped
Potatoes, peeled & chopped
1/2 Onion, sliced or diced
3 Cloves Garlic, minced
1tsp Ginger, minced
1tsp turmeric
1tsp cumin seed
1tsp mustard seed (black)
1tsp chili powder
Garam Masala


MISE

Chop Potatoes
Slice Onion
Mince Ginger
Mince Garlic
Butcher Chicken


COOK

Dutch oven
Medium high
add oil
add onion
add garlic
add ginger
Saut√© until golden
add masala
add turmeric
add cumin seed
add chili powder
Toast
add chicken
add salt
mix well
Cook for 15min
Add potatoes/plantain
cover and cook for 20min
garnish with cilantro